**Problem:** No HTTP security headers are set. This exposes the app to clickjacking, MIME sniffing, XSS, and other header-based attacks. Express also advertises itself via the `X-Powered-By: Express` header by default.

**Fix:** Use [Helmet.js](https://helmetjs.github.io/):

