app.listen(PORT, () => console.log(`Server running on port ${PORT}`));
```

---

### 10. 🟡 No Security Logging or Monitoring (OWASP A09)

**Issue:** There is no request logging. Failed auth attempts, unusual traffic spikes, or attacks will be completely invisible.

**Fix:** Add structured request logging (e.g., [`morgan`](https://www.npmjs.com/package/morgan)) and consider integrating with a SIEM or alerting system:

```js
